long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: For Penn Students, the new tool for your schedules, Path @ Penn, does not have a way to export your class calendar. This tool allows you to upload to either google calendar or download a file for your apple calendar! Just click the google extension when on your Path @ Penn page with the primary cart open, and this should give you your schedule!
